{"tid":2375445,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"係依家 big data 資訊年代，hku bsc(im) 算係未比人發現嘅平民神科","createTime":"2021-01-22T05:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T05:13:31.000Z","uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8a66e4f37d784a73fae0755f2b97c44f9964f18b","tid":2375445,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"Bsc(Im) Information management 雖然係 under education fac ，其實都算幾 IT 。雖然<span class=\"red\"><strong>原意</strong></span>係比人將來做圖書館助理/搞下 e-learning。讀完 information management 除咗中小學 e-learning/ICT教師/圖書館技術人員，仲可以投身 data science/fintech 行業 。算係進可攻退可守嘅科黎。重點係收分唔高，但前途無可限量。<br />\n<br />\ncore courses:<br />\nInformation management foundations (6 credits)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"purple\">Information retrieval</span></strong> (6 credits)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"purple\">Project management</span></strong> (6 credits)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"purple\">Database systems </span></strong>(6 credits)<br />\nInformation society issues and policy (6 credits)<br />\nInformation organisation and content management (6 credits)<br />\nProfessional experience (6 credits)<br />\nProject (6 credits)<br />\n<br />\n都係一半 technical 嘢 e.g. database system (即係寫下 SQL) / information retrieval ，又有文科 e.g. information society issues 。到 intern/grad interview 時無論 technical test 定吹水都可以輕鬆應付<br />\n<br />\nelectives:<br />\nKnowledge management (6 credits)<br />\nDigital libraries: principles and applications (6 credits)<br />\nRecords management (6 credits)<br />\nUser-based systems analysis (6 credits)<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Data warehousing and data mining </strong></span>(6 credits)<br />\nElectronic commerce (6 credits)<br />\nWeb development, users and management (6 credits)<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Management information systems</strong></span> (6 credits)<br />\nFundamentals of object-oriented programming (6 credits)<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Multimedia and human-computer interaction</strong></span> (6 credits)<br />\nIntroduction to statistics and quantitative data analysis (6 credits)<br />\n<br />\n比 computer science 更著重 practical issue 同埋都幾 tech 下。Human computer interface 同 data warehousing 都係近年熱門技能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a743b9cb56cb5c60ba06bb853ad19f284748ae8f","tid":2375445,"uid":381575,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"狀元揀唔到嘅科<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a485b5b3de0456eed165517a13477b2d0f6e41f7","tid":2375445,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a743b9cb56cb5c60ba06bb853ad19f284748ae8f","tid":2375445,"uid":381575,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"狀元揀唔到嘅科<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死"},{"pid":"5386148933a4f132037034e82f69df9fc7fcd905","tid":2375445,"uid":23445,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"雞肋科<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠cs hardcore, 吹水又唔夠bba佬勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚讀完比人屈死都似"},{"pid":"e16036c5c63d4dc1b757b8e7ef35e2a5522b30b2","tid":2375445,"uid":342698,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"Hku教學質素差<br />\nNotes差<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"076ee8df520482e69922d30c0e80d955136e4af0","tid":2375445,"uid":88592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:29:23.00